// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-0460 — Mass File Rename (ransomed)
// Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: ecb318b9-7902-595f-997f-5c4416ed5387

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
